text: Ingus Veips (born 12 December 1969) is a Latvian former cyclist. He competed in the track time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Latvian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Latvia Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Madona
